<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idc2827eb5-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idc2827eb6-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Prior sections 503 and 504 were renumbered sections 1503 and 1504 of this title, respectively.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Provisions similar to those in this section were contained in section 210(c)(2), (3) of this title prior to repeal by <ref href="/us/pl/102/83/s2/a">Pub. L. 102–83, § 2(a)</ref>.</p>
</note>
